00:01:35.875 --> 00:01:38.815
Cancer is the leading cause of death in New Zealand.

40
00:01:39.685 --> 00:01:42.375
It's therefore only right that our health system responds

41
00:01:42.375 --> 00:01:45.695
to this by having an agency whose sole focus is

42
00:01:45.695 --> 00:01:48.775
to improve outcomes for all who face a cancer diagnosis

