82
00:03:40.255 --> 00:03:43.455
to improve prevention, early detection, treatment,

83
00:03:44.055 --> 00:03:45.695
survivorship and pa, palliative

84
00:03:45.695 --> 00:03:47.655
and end of life care with equity

85
00:03:47.795 --> 00:03:50.375
