179
00:08:15.755 --> 00:08:17.835
I will now give you a summary of the current state

180
00:08:17.975 --> 00:08:20.435
of cancer in New Zealand based on the LA latest

181
00:08:20.545 --> 00:08:21.795
data available to us.

182
00:08:22.675 --> 00:08:23.855
So let's start with some good news.

183
00:08:23.855 --> 00:08:26.455
First, in New Zealand, the chance

184
00:08:26.455 --> 00:08:29.215
of dying from cancer has been declining for decades.

185
00:08:30.195 --> 00:08:32.615
The mortality rate, which which is the number

186
00:08:32.615 --> 00:08:35.695
of cancer deaths per a hundred thousand people adjusted for,

187
00:08:35.835 --> 00:08:40.175
uh, for age, has dropped from 145 per a hundred thousand in

