that's almost a 30% decrease.

190
00:08:46.555 --> 00:08:48.655
And most of that is coming from improvements in

191
00:08:48.655 --> 00:08:51.055
how we screen for and treat cancer.

192
00:08:52.445 --> 00:08:53.905
The chance of surviving cancer

193
00:08:53.955 --> 00:08:58.245
after five years has improved from 58% in

194
00:08:58.445 --> 00:09:01.365
