195
00:09:02.475 --> 00:09:03.525
That translates roughly

196
00:09:03.625 --> 00:09:08.505
to 3000 more people alive every year in 2025.

197
00:09:08.685 --> 00:09:11.105
Faster cancer treatment wait times have been nudging up

198
00:09:11.105 --> 00:09:12.705
towards the 90% target

199
00:09:13.805 --> 00:09:15.865
and the last 18 months, hundreds

200
00:09:15.865 --> 00:09:17.105
of millions have been invested

201
00:09:17.245 --> 00:09:20.145
to make many more cancer medicines publicly available

202
00:09:20.245 --> 00:09:21.825
to thousands of cancer patients.

203
00:09:23.385 --> 00:09:25.575
Other large investments have been made in expanding

204
00:09:25.575 --> 00:09:28.535
radiation treatment capacity through new centers in FANG

205
