research at the levels needed.

244
00:11:21.125 --> 00:11:23.145
The state of our physical infrastructure is mixed,

245
00:11:23.325 --> 00:11:24.385
and a number of hospitals

246
00:11:24.385 --> 00:11:27.505
and cancer centers are in serious need of investment.

247
00:11:28.925 --> 00:11:31.985
And our need to fund increasingly expensive diagnostics

248
00:11:31.985 --> 00:11:35.545
and therapeutics that are coming down the pipe will continue

249
00:11:35.545 --> 00:11:38.225
to put major pressure on our fiscal resources.

250
00:11:39.725 --> 00:11:40.905
Having highlighted the wins

251
00:11:40.905 --> 00:11:43.585
and remaining challenges, it's important to recognize some

252
00:11:43.585 --> 00:11:45.425
of the exciting opportunities on the horizon.

253
00:11:47.395 --> 00:11:49.475
A coordinated strategy for the elimination

254
